  <summary date="2021-09-15T20:24:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Natural Cosmetics Act 

This bill prohibits the sale of a cosmetics product that uses the term natural on its packaging or labeling unless the product meets certain requirements. The bill also authorizes the Food and Drug Administration to request or order a recall of a cosmetics product that violates these labeling requirements.</summary>
